high_descs: pick up kettle on left side of stove
wash kettle in sink, pick up kettle from sink
walk right to face cabinets to right of sink
put kettle in bottom right cabinet
anns.task_desc: put a washed kettle in a cabinet

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the wall then turn right and walk to the stove that will be on your left and turn left to face it when you get there.
Pick up the kettle that's in front of you on the middle burner.
Turn right and walk to the counter then take a step to your right so you're facing the sink.
Wash the kettle in the sink and then pick it back up and shut off the water.
Turn right and walk to the counter then turn left and take a step backwards.,
Open the cupboard in front of you furthest to the right and put the kettle down there before closing the door.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean kettle in the cupboard.

high_descs: Turn around, hang left at the chair towards the wall, turn right and walk to the cook top range on the left.
Pick up the tea kettle in the middle of the cook top range.
Turn around, hang a left at the counter, turn right at the next counter and walk to the sink on the left.
Put the tea kettle inside the sink, rinse it for a few seconds and pick it back up.
Turn right, hang a right at the fridge and turn around to face the cabinets next to the dishwasher.
Open the tall cabinet to the right of the dishwasher, put the rinsed tea kettle inside and close the door.
anns.task_desc: Place a rinsed tea kettle in a cabinet.
